  "title": "PROJECT ENGINEER (C&S)",
  "description": "<p><strong>PROJECT ENGINEER (C&S)</strong><br /></p><p><strong>Job Description</strong>:</p><ul><li>Review construction drawings and calculations for buildings, foundations and other infrastructure</li><li>Perform site planning, coordination & inspection relating to the construction project so as to ensure that project completion timeline, requirements and budget are met</li><li>Provide technical guidance and solutions to site engineers and construction teams</li><li>Update the progress of structural works in the Progress Reports</li><li>Maintain the proper documentation of inspection forms and other follow-up inspections from RE</li><li>Prepare structural reports, method statements, and engineering documentation</li><li>To ensure works are in compliance with safety and quality procedures and within standard workmanship requirements</li></ul><p><br /><strong>Requirements</strong>:</p><ul><li>Minimum Degree in Civil Engineering (recognized by PE Board of Singapore)</li><li>At least 3 years of local relevant experience in Construction industry; HDB preferred</li><li>Good analytical, communication and interpersonal skills</li></ul><p>Suitable candidates are encouraged to apply this position via Apply Now button or email to <strong>Career@kah.com.sg</strong></p><p>Only shortlisted applicants will be notified.</p>",
